{{Quote|You mean they're intelligent?''"<br />"''Not much more so than most other animals, but smart enough. They care for one another and have their own kind of wisdom.|Isolder and Luke Skywalker discuss the Blue Desert People|<ref name="The Courtship of Princess Leia">''[[The Courtship of Princess Leia]]''</ref>}}
The '''Blue Desert People''' were a group of [[Kwi]] who lived in the [[Great Desert of Dathomir]] on the planet [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. This group gave [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Isolder]] a ride through the desert during their search for [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] in [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]].<ref name="The Courtship of Princess Leia" />

